==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mo
<hw>Mo</hw> <pr>(m⟦omac⟧)</pr>, <pos>a., adv., & n.</pos>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>moe</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[AS.
<ets>m⟦amac⟧</ets>. See <er>More</er>.]</ety> <def>More; -- usually,
more in number.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An hundred thousand <qex>mo</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Likely to find <qex>mo</qex> to commend than to imitate it.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

